  <!-- EN: Wolfein AIPT Stun Rifle -->
  <W_Weapon_AR_AIPTStungun.label>沃芬AIPT高斯步枪</W_Weapon_AR_AIPTStungun.label>
  <!-- EN: A MegaCorp experimental weapon that uses electromagnetic force between rails to accelerate projectiles to incredible speeds, designed to destroy anomalous objects. The specially designed projectiles are capable of causing temporary disorientation to the target upon impact. -->
